# Build context is the repo root but only apps/web is built. Keep the context lean
# and make CERTAIN no credentials or local build output are ever sent to the daemon.

# secrets — never ship these into a build context
**/.secrets/
**/gcp-key.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/run-with-secrets.sh

# vcs + tooling scratch
.git/
.codex-lanes/
**/.DS_Store

# node + next build output (rebuilt inside the image)
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/.next-verify/
**/out/
**/dist/

# unrelated apps — only apps/web is built, drop the heavy siblings from the context
apps/grading-cre/
apps/strategy-vault/
apps/tee-runner/
apps/uniswap-lp/
apps/x402-facilitator/
apps/honeycomb-api/
apps/honeycomb-mcp/

# docs / misc
**/*.md
**/coverage/
